casharka day 2 waan dawaday concepts ficana wan ka haystaa waxana ka mid ah

---------------------------------------------------------------------------
platform independent = byte code waxuu ku run gareysmi karaa operational system kasta

waxan ubaahannahay in source codeka loobadalo machine code si computer uu ufahmo
compilerka waxuu kaa caawinaayaa in loobadalo codeka midshaqeynaya
executable code = waa urur amaro ah oo computerka lasiiyo
java waaa platform  independent lkn java vartual machine waa dependent

jdk = java development kit =  waxey ku siineysaa environment aa ku develop gareyn laheyd kuna run gareyn lehed programkaaga javada

jre = java run time environmrnt = waa installgareenta package kaas oo ku siinaaya environment aa kiliya ku run gareynkarto programkaaga

qodoboda ugu caansan ee aan ku bartay waxaa kamid ah :
>>primitive data Types in java :
 ineger
 character
 float
 double
 long
 booelan
coments waxaa loo adeegsadaa in codeka explanation laga biyo ama in codeka la egnore gareyo ama loo diido in la run gareey.
>condition ka oo ah in xaalad lagu xiro anagoo adeegsanayna :
 ..if-if-else-else
>loop oo ah
Loops in Java waxaa loo isticmaalo in lagu fuliyo qayb gaar ah oo programka ka mid ah si isdaba joog ah haddii xaalad la siiyay ay qiimayso inay true tahay.
marka la samaynayno loopska waxa la adeegsan karaa
..for loop:waxaan  isticmaali karnaa marka tirada soo noqnoqto ama ay xadidantahay ama la yaqaano.
..while loop: waxaa la adeegsada aydana marka aan la ogeyn inta jeer  uu loopku soconayo.
.do while loop.